    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : [REDACTED] DATE: August 29, 1952",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM : [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "ALLEGEDLY CITED BY MR. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "WEST PALM BEACH, FLORIDA",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "By letter of August 26, 1952, the Air Force requested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "that we examine the cap of Mr. [REDACTED], a scoutmaster",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "at West Palm Beach, Florida, who claims that he observed an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "unidentified flying object in a desolate area. He reported",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "that upon his investigation, a [unclear] object 30 feet in diameter",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "hovered over his head and shot a \"red blob\" which caused him to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "lose consciousness. The cap has some holes burned in it and it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "is reported that the hair on Desuergers' arms was singed. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Air Force requested that we determine, if possible, from any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "residues left the nature of the residual material.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "The Air Force desires an oral report on this tonight.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "We have finished the examination and are preparing to advise the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Air Force as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "1. There is no residue which would permit a determination",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "as to the nature of the material which caused the burns in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "cap. In addition to the obvious burns, there is one minute burned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "area which is probably too small to have been caused intentionally",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "but more likely by a small hot ember.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "2. The bill and a large part of the edges of the cap",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "are singed but the singeing is not uniform as would be expected",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "if it had been caused at one time by a single flash of flame. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "front edge of the cap bill is more severely singed than other",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "portions of the cap. This condition would not be expected if the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "source of the flame was directly overhead.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "3. When the cap is observed from the front, the left",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "edge of the insignia and the fold in the blue cloth, there is an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "absence of singeing noted under the fold suggesting the possibility",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "that the cap was not being worn when the singeing took place.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "It is noted that this fold \"smooths out\" when the cap is placed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "on the head.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "RECOMMENDATION: That in response to the request, of Colonel [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "of the Air Force, it is recommended that he be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "orally advised of the above.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "[unclear] RH [unclear] 221-03XDN1 62-83874-315",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
